Subject: Re: final call for revisions for this round

> Playing Reprise cf. *Playin
> Playing Jam cf. *Playin*

I think that these would be as precise as necessary.

Playing in the Band  -- the entire song (all 4 to 45 minutes)
Playing  		the first lyrics
Playing Jam		Playing based space unattached to Playing or Playing 
			Reprise 
Main Ten Jam		pre-Playing Playing Jams
Playing Reprise		the second lyrics

I cannot think of a real good reason to exclude these, it shouldn't be 
that difficult to track them all.  And if we're going to bother to 
catalogue all the Day Jobs, we sould track these pieces too.

Of course, this begs the question of what to do with the Dark Star's and 
Uncle John's Band's and Other One's (and Me & My Uncles) that are 
similarly split.

